g.text: def backward(self, upstream_gradients): self.x_local_gradients = self.w.T self.w_local_gradients = self.x.T self.b_local_gradients = np.ones((self.x.shape[0], 1)).T self.x_gradients = np.dot(upstream_gradients, self.x_local_gradients) self.w_gradients = np.dot(self.w_local_gradients, upstream_gradients) self.b_gradients = np.dot(self.b_local_gradients, upstream_gradients) return self.x_gradients
